To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private GravestoneDoji _gravestonedoji;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_gravestonedoji = GravestoneDoji(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_gravestonedoji.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "gravestonedoji", _gravestonedoji.Current.Value);
}
